[center]Hi!

I bring to you this preset about Claire Redfield from the Resident Evil Game.

This is my first mod so please be gentle :3

Any feedback is welcome.



[b][u]:: Requirements ::[/u]


• Race: Nord
[/b]• RaceMenu
• CBBE
• SKSE
• Hair  - [url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QjIIlIJ20ko]SG Hair Pack[/url]
• Eyes - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes Of Beauty[/url]
• [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows[/url]
• Skin Texture - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures Renewal[/url]
• [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52841/?]Freckle Mania[/url]

[u][b]:: Installation ::[/b][/u]

Put the ClaireRedfield.jslot \data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets folder ;)

[u][b]:: Attention ::[/b][/u]

This mod is only for personal use. You can't make any follower with this preset without my permission.
Claire Redfield character by (c) Capcom.

If you one a follower with this preset you can use [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54509/?]Familiar Faces by Verteiron[/url] <3
